	  PropertyConfigurator files.

2002-07-02 20:32  bastiaan

	* ChangeLog, THANKS, include/log4cpp/Configurator.hh,
	  include/log4cpp/ConfiguratorSkeleton.hh,
	  include/log4cpp/Makefile.am,
